@startuml
title ConstructFlow - 3-Layer Software Architecture
left to right direction
skinparam roundcorner 8
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultTextAlignment center

rectangle "Presentation" as Presentation
rectangle "Business Logic" as Business
rectangle "Persistence" as Persistence
rectangle "Specific DBMS Processing\n(Firebase SDK Calls)" as DBMS
database "DB\n(Firestore + Storage + Auth)" as DB
rectangle "Domain Objects\nUser, Organization, Project, Task,\nBlueprint, Material, Allocation, Transaction" as Domain

Presentation --> Business : Request object
Business --> Presentation : Result (collection of objects)

Business --> Persistence : Request object
Persistence --> Business : Result (collection of objects)

Persistence <--> DBMS
DBMS <--> DB

Domain -up-> Presentation
Domain -up-> Business
Domain -up-> Persistence

note bottom of Presentation
Files:

src/main.jsx
src/App.jsx
src/pages/*
src/components/*
src/styles/*
src/App.css
src/index.css
end note
note bottom of Business
Files:

src/contexts/AuthContext.jsx
src/utils/inventoryDomain.js
src/utils/materialsConstants.js
end note
note bottom of Persistence
Files:

src/firebase.js
src/utils/materialsRepository.js
end note

@enduml